1
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:07,840
Haoran

2
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:10,040
I'm not so sure about this plan.

3
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:13,040
That immersive cooking takes forever.

4
00:01:13,319 --> 00:01:15,159
Stewing soup, proofing dough, how long does that take?

5
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,040
Gele,

6
