No, no.

11
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,640
Just let me explain.

12
00:01:28,439 --> 00:01:29,640
Cities are developing fast these days.

13
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,280
Sometimes when people watch livestreams,

14
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:32,680
