15
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:34,359
It's to relieve stress.

16
00:01:35,719 --> 00:01:36,079
Just think about it.

17
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,680
You get home from work,

18
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:39,359
