19
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,719
listening to the sound of a knife chopping veggies,

20
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,159
and then you watch

21
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:44,760
the flames inside the wood stove.

22
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,319
Isn't that better than sleeping pills?

23
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,000
Chopping sounds can put you to sleep?

24
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:49,760
Yep.

25
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:51,719
You can also listen to the crackling firewood,

26
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:52,799
the sound of

27
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,359
deep frying.

28
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,159
This slow pace in our mountains

29
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,599
is a luxury to them.

30
00:01:58,439 --> 00:01:59,480
What about the savage reviews?

31
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,359
If they trash us in front of thousands,

32
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:03,000
our reputation's done for.

33
