What people online fear most isn't bad reviews,

35
00:02:07,439 --> 00:02:08,240
it's fakeness.

36
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:09,599
Look,

37
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,919
if we hired someone

38
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,879
to praise our village to the skies,

39
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,439
netizens would think it's fake.

40
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:15,360
Shills.

41
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:16,919
But,

42
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,199
if a picky

43
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:18,680
influencer

44
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:19,919
gives a few critiques,

45
00:02:20,159 --> 00:02:21,639
and finishes with "not bad,"

46
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,719
that one line

47
00:02:23,199 --> 00:02:23,879
is worth a million.

48
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,639
Kid, that's a good move.

49
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:29,039
That's called having faith and confidence in ourselves.

50
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,840
You're betting on Jimei's cooking skills.

51
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,599
I have confidence in Jimei's cooking.

52
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:35,439
Right?

53
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:36,080
Alright.

54
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:38,080
As long as it gets our village's

55
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:38,759
tourism going,

56
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:40,000
these old bones of mine

57
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:40,960
will go all in.

58
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:41,560
Alright.

59
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,039
Let's go.

60
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:48,479
How'd you sleep last night?

61
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:49,719
Pretty well.

62
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:51,319
You didn't catch a cold, did you?

63
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,120
Thanks for asking.

64
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,759
Both experts are here.

65
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,080
