Not interested.

67
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,599
I haven't even said it yet.

68
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:02,879
I know what you're going to say.

69
00:03:03,759 --> 00:03:05,199
A food livestream promo, right?

70
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,120
Not interested.

71
00:03:07,759 --> 00:03:08,680
I work with plants.

72
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:09,639
That's not my thing.

73
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,560
This is a

74
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,159
great chance to develop the under-forest economy.

75
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:13,520
Right?

76
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:16,319
Fine.

77
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,280
I'll join in, on one condition.

78
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,439
Include some content in the livestream

79
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:22,080
