80
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,360
Sure, pack it full!

81
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:24,520
We'll include it throughout.

82
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:25,560
Then it's a deal.

83
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:25,879
Okay.

84
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,080
I'm full. I'm heading up the mountain to collect samples.

85
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:28,520
Okay.

86
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:29,840
Where's Tashi?

87
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:31,840
He had something to do. He'll be here later.

88
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:33,639
He's slacking off again.

89
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:34,719
No, no, no.

90
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:35,919
Drolma's roof is leaking.

91
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:36,919
He's a kind-hearted guy.

92
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:37,800
Everyone in the village goes to him for this kind of stuff.

93
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,319
Alright then.

94
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:42,719
I'm off.

95
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,240
Nana, look.

96
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:47,960
Not interested.

97
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,759
There's a fee.

98
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,120
Two thousand per session.

99
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,520
Three sessions total, Nana.

100
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,800
What do you mean, two thousand per session?

101
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:57,919
We're putting together an under-forest economy

102
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:58,599
