103
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,759
You can help me out with it.

104
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:00,759
Still not interested.

105
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,680
Qianqian.

106
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:04,800
Qianqian.

107
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,439
Can you do it or not?

108
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:13,120
Ajia, that's the third time you've asked.

109
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,719
Then I'll ask a fourth time.

110
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,040
Can you do it?

111
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,519
If I can't, who else could you ask?

112
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,079
Oh, plenty of people.

113
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,439
I could ask Haoran.

114
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,240
He can't even close a window properly.

115
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,240
Then there's Gele.

116
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:29,759
His back is bad.

117
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:31,319
