121
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:41,720
Have lunch at my place. I'm stewing meat.

122
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:42,959
No need.

123
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:44,240
I'm heading into the mountains at noon.

124
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,279
Up the mountain?

125
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,360
You're going to keep Medo company?

126
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:52,759
How do you know?

127
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,639
The whole village is talking about it.

128
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:56,839
They say you're her guide,

129
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:58,639
and you stewed her precious lingzhi.

130
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:00,240
Now you owe her eighteen thousand.

131
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:02,160
Word sure travels fast with you.

132
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,279
You bet.

133
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:08,639
How could you let her go into the mountains alone

134
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,839
just to come fix my roof?

135
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:12,920
She's been roaming the mountains since she was a kid.

136
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:13,720
She won't get lost.

137
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:15,199
Won't get lost.

138
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,759
Then why use a drone to watch her?

139
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:19,360
Buzzing around all over the place.

140
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,439
Gave me a headache.

141
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,040
I'm just taking a look.

142
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,360
Just a look.

143
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,000
Or is it

144
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:27,480
that you just want to see her?

145
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:30,920
Ajia, you...

146
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,600
Tashi.

147
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,319
Your ears are turning red.

148
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:34,199
I...

149
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,279
I, I got sunburned.

150
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,040
My, my ears...

151
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,319
Sunburned.

152
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:39,600
Sunburned.

153
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:05,920
Tashi.

154
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,519
Why aren't you here yet?

155
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,319
If you don't come soon, I'll get mad.

156
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,199
And you won't like me when I'm mad.

157
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,759
At least you have a conscience.

158
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,079
Tashi.

159
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,560
Have some apples.

160
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:55,879
Still watching?

161
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:04,560
Something's wrong!

162
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,000
What happened?

163
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,480
Ajia, I'll come help you later.

164
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,639
She fell. I have to go check on her.

165
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:10,600
Be careful.

166
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:22,720
Tashi!

167
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,120
Tashi.

168
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:14,800
Where are you hurt?

169
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:17,959
My foot hurts.

170
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:22,920
Easy, easy, easy.

171
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,039
Did you hurt anywhere else?

172
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:36,919
Nothing's broken.

173
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:38,279
Probably a pulled ligament.

174
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,440
Need to ice it.

175
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,360
How do you know it's not broken?

176
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,759
I've carried seventeen or eighteen

177
00:08:42,759 --> 00:08:43,879
