240
00:11:23,279 --> 00:11:23,960
Don't come alone.

241
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:26,000
Weren't you busy today?

242
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:28,759
Today was my fault.

243
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:31,000
From now on, you come first.

244
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:37,240
I mean,

245
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,840
I'm afraid if you get hurt again,

246
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,360
I'll owe you even more.

247
00:11:43,879 --> 00:11:44,399
I get it.
